data.text:
The Gods of Mars

I truly enjoyed this book ! The adventure is great.... but what

more important is the morality of the book... Captain John Carter is

Gentleman of the 1st Order... he is True, Honest, Faithful, Loyal...

its inspiring to read ! For this reason alone I would recommend this book,

especially for young folks... as an alternative to the Grand Theft Auto

video games and the like....
